the protesters in the unofficial may day protest 
i saw stalin portraits nicholas ii portraits he said 
slogans were heard that ceausescus destiny is in store for some 
people referring to romanian leader nicolae ceausescu executed 
after a summary trial dec 25 
that was really unfortunate yakovlev said anybody would 
treat these slogans as an insult 
