jurors in the murder trial of a man accused in 
the bensonhurst racial slaying told the judge saturday that theyd 
reached verdicts on some charges but couldnt agree on others 
judge thadeus owens instructed jurors in the trial of keith 
mondello 19 to retire for the evening telling them to get a good 
