the italian officials of the foundry to determine if they knew the 
purpose and destination of the components 
police said they have not yet made any arrests 
the agency said italian investigators are in constant contact 
with other european police agencies in an attempt to determine if 
iraq has succeeded in importing other parts of the weapon 
