nightly news for five years gartner issued a statement praising 
wheatley but saying he thinks its time to take the broadcast in 
a different direction wheatley will remain at nbc news 
in a brief interview brokaw called wheatley one of the good 
guys a tireless worker and a great friend and colleague im 
going to miss him 
